Three styles, like triangle
Ranged, Magic, Melee
Magic weak to ranged, strong against Melee
Melee weak to Magic, strong against Ranged
Range weak to melee, strong against magic

Player levels up, gains 3 trait points

MELEE TRAITS
short/longswords
clubs and maces
spears and halberds

MAGIC TRAITS
enchantments (healing, boosts)
purple aura (defensive magics like summoning, repelling)
dismemberment (offensive spells)

RANGE TRAITS
thrown weapons (knives, darts, javelins)
bows
crossbows, ballistae

GENERAL TRAITS
blocking
critical strikes
duel-wielding

SKILLS
Fishing
Mining
Strength
Vitality
Magic
Dexterity
Crafting
Blacksmithing